NOTE ON SCOPE

The MIT license above covers only the C# application code, scripts, CI and
documentation authored in this repository.

It does NOT cover Codec 2. Codec 2 is a separate project by David Rowe and
contributors, licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License v2.1
(LGPL-2.1). It is included as a git submodule (codec2/) and the native runtime
libcodec2.dll (in src/native/) is built from it. The player loads libcodec2.dll
dynamically (P/Invoke); the DLL can be rebuilt or replaced from the submodule
via scripts/build-native.ps1.

Codec 2 source and license:  https://github.com/drowe67/codec2
The native library is pinned to commit 9f5e2de (the last commit before the 450
and 450PWB modes were removed upstream).
